      <title>墨西哥比索在选举中获胜后跌幅扩大至 2%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/mexican-peso-extends-loss-to-2-after-landslide-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥比索延续跌势，兑美元下跌逾 2%，因初步选举结果显示，执政党以压倒性优势获胜，这可能使其有权加强国家对经济的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/mexican-peso-extends-loss-to-2-after-landslide-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
