      <title>养老院运营商 LaVie Care Centers 申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/nursing-home-operator-lavie-care-centers-files-for-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LaVie Care Centers LLC 以 ​​Consulate Health Care 等名义经营着 43 家养老院和辅助生活设施，由于该行业面临高昂的劳动力成本、较低的入住率和不均衡的报销率等问题，该公司成为最新一家申请第 11 章破产保护的连锁企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/nursing-home-operator-lavie-care-centers-files-for-bankruptcy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:36:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
